title: Cemeteries, Florida, 2008
name: Cemeteries, Florida, 2008
description: This dataset contains 2008 Cemetery location information for the State of Florida. It is a combination of cemeteries and other types of burial ground locations from 17 different data sources including; county specific cemetery locations, parcel centroids, GNIS, SHPO cemetery centroids, SuperPage cemetery address locations, etc. This dataset contains fields denoting the location, and other information for cemeteries located in Florida. This layer is an update of the previously released FGDL layer "GC_CEMETERY_SEP05".
